Repeat: P2, sl 1 wyib, k5, sl 1 wyib, p2
K2, sl 1 wyif, p5, sl 1 wyif, k2

p2; drop slipped stitch to front of work, k2, pick up dropped stitch and knit it, k1, sl 2 wyib, drop slipped stitch to front of work, slip the same 2 stitches back to the left-hand needle, pick up dropped stitch and knit it; k2, p2
P2, k2, sl 1 wyib, k1, sl 1 wyib, k2, p2
K2, sl 1 wyif, p1, sl 1 wyif, p2, k2

p2; slip 2 wyib, drop slipped stitch to front of work, slip the same 2 stitches back to the left-hand needle, pick up dropped stitch and knit it, k3, drop slipped stitch to front of work, k2, pick up dropped stitch and knit it; p2
